{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1271537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我错了，不是康德主张，是康德提到的一个点。", "timestamp": 1615898802, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1271540, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不知道是否是康德的原文呐。但是看起来，意思是，我们每个人之所以要过道德的生活，是因为我们具有道德的义务，而不是过的道德能让我们得到好处。我们不能问，我做一个道德的人有什么回报，因为做道德的人，本身就是实践理性的义务。", "timestamp": 1615898819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1271544, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1、这不像是康德的原话\n2、尝试按照康德哲学去理解的话，这里的“责任”应当是指“义务”，因为在康德看来人作为道德主体是自律的，即人自身为自己已然规定了行为的准则，因此遵守道德对人而言是一项义务", "timestamp": 1615898880, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1271554, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我猜是个蹩脚的翻译者强行按照格言的形式去翻译or总结康德的意思2333", "timestamp": 1615898977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1271575, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 确实", "timestamp": 1615899151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1271582, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 阿哈哈哈哈应该是这样的！ 我大概懂了，谢谢alice和bob！", "timestamp": 1615899288, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1271588, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 250768, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一说一，能看见真正的哲学交流洞还是挺惊讶的", "timestamp": 1615899339, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 250768, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "康德主张的“有责任去具有责任”是什么意思呀？我彻底懵了😭", "timestamp": 1615898647, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1615899593, "url": "", "vote": {}}}